{"type":"text","timestamp":1781087784606,"sessionID":"ses_14ee58b2fffeP6pDsoVmcnH3I0","part":{"id":"prt_eb11ac4cd00103KzsvOpeJsBHi","messageID":"msg_eb11abef3001U1m2MSNITB0Wll","sessionID":"ses_14ee58b2fffeP6pDsoVmcnH3I0","type":"text","text":"This is a single-collection CRUD admin page (shifts table + add form), so the Auto Patterns Dashboard is the mandatory path. The app namespace is `@mirivo/my-appbw7bhj`. I'll scaffold the Data Collection first, then the Dashboard Page.","time":{"start":1781087782093,"end":1781087784602}}}
