  "job_input": "[{\"role\":\"USER\",\"text\":\"Build a dashboard page that lets store owners manage employee shifts. The page should have a table where each row is a shift with these fields: employee name, date and hours. The store owner must be able to add new shifts to the table.\"},{\"role\":\"ASSISTANT\",\"text\":\"Manage employee shifts effortlessly with this dashboard. View all shifts in a table and easily add new ones to keep your records up to date.  \\n<<{\\\"widget\\\":\\\"BLUEPRINT_WIDGET\\\",\\\"data\\\":{\\\"extensions\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"DASHBOARD_PAGE\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Shift Manager\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Admin dashboard page where store owners view a table of shifts (employee name, date, hours) and add new shift records, reading from and writing to the shifts collection.\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"DATA_COLLECTION\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Employee Shifts Data\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Collection storing shift records with fields for employee name, shift date, and hours, used by the dashboard page for listing and adding shifts.\\\"}],\\\"keyFeatures\\\":[\\\"Dashboard table of all employee shifts\\\",\\\"Fields per shift: employee name, date, hours\\\",\\\"Ability to add new shifts from the dashboard\\\",\\\"Persistent storage of shifts in a CMS collection\\\"],\\\"appName\\\":\\\"ShiftCommand\\\",\\\"dataString\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"0144d7ba-ee15-44ef-86b7-4cc1507ac94f\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"appName\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ShiftCommand\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"summary\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Create a dedicated dashboard page for store owners to manage employee shifts, backed by a data collection that stores each shift record. The dashboard page displays shifts in a table (employee name, date, hours) and allows adding new shifts, which are persisted to the collection for ongoing management.\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"extensions\\\\\\\":[{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"DASHBOARD_PAGE\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Shift Manager\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Admin dashboard page where store owners view a table of shifts (employee name, date, hours) and add new shift records, reading from and writing to the shifts collection.\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"DATA_COLLECTION\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Employee Shifts Data\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Collection storing shift records with fields for employee name, shift date, and hours, used by the dashboard page for listing and adding shifts.\\\\\\\"}],\\\\\\\"keyFeatures\\\\\\\":[\\\\\\\"Dashboard table of all employee shifts\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"Fields per shift: employee name, date, hours\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"Ability to add new shifts from the dashboard\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"Persistent storage of shifts in a CMS collection\\\\\\\"]}\\\",\\\"version\\\":\\\"1.0\\\",\\\"summary\\\":\\\"Create a dedicated dashboard page for store owners to manage employee shifts, backed by a data collection that stores each shift record. The dashboard page displays shifts in a table (employee name, date, hours) and allows adding new shifts, which are persisted to the collection for ongoing management.\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"0144d7ba-ee15-44ef-86b7-4cc1507ac94f\\\"},\\\"config\\\":{\\\"borderless\\\":true,\\\"readAloud\\\":\\\"Welcome to ShiftCommand, your tool for managing employee shifts with ease. Here’s what you can do: The Shift Manager dashboard page displays a table of all employee shifts, showing details like the employee name, the shift date, and the number of hours worked. From this dashboard, you can also add new shift records directly. All shift data is stored in the Employee Shifts Data collection, ensuring that your records are saved and accessible for ongoing management. To get started, you can say things like, \\\\\\\"Show me the shift table,\\\\\\\" or \\\\\\\"Add a new shift.\\\\\\\" Let me know how I can assist you!\\\",\\\"textOnly\\\":\\\"Shift Manager is an admin dashboard page designed for store owners to manage employee shifts efficiently. The dashboard displays a table containing all shift records, including fields for employee name, shift date, and hours worked. Store owners can view existing shifts and add new shift records, which are stored persistently in the Employee Shifts Data collection for ongoing management. This ensures accurate tracking and organization of employee work schedules.\\\",\\\"userLanguage\\\":\\\"en\\\"}}>>\"},{\"role\":\"USER\",\"text\":\"<HIDDEN>Build it {{{{Blueprint data (\\\"id\\\" refers to blueprint): {\\\"id\\\":\\\"0144d7ba-ee15-44ef-86b7-4cc1507ac94f\\\",\\\"appName\\\":\\\"ShiftCommand\\\",\\\"summary\\\":\\\"Create a dedicated dashboard page for store owners to manage employee shifts, backed by a data collection that stores each shift record. The dashboard page displays shifts in a table (employee name, date, hours) and allows adding new shifts, which are persisted to the collection for ongoing management.\\\",\\\"extensions\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"DASHBOARD_PAGE\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Shift Manager\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Admin dashboard page where store owners view a table of shifts (employee name, date, hours) and add new shift records, reading from and writing to the shifts collection.\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"DATA_COLLECTION\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Employee Shifts Data\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Collection storing shift records with fields for employee name, shift date, and hours, used by the dashboard page for listing and adding shifts.\\\"}],\\\"keyFeatures\\\":[\\\"Dashboard table of all employee shifts\\\",\\\"Fields per shift: employee name, date, hours\\\",\\\"Ability to add new shifts from the dashboard\\\",\\\"Persistent storage of shifts in a CMS collection\\\"]}}}}}{{</HIDDEN>\"},{\"role\":\"ASSISTANT\",\"text\":\"\"}]",
